# Meal Picker App

A macOS app that helps you decide what to eat by randomly selecting meal items from your favorite restaurants.

## Features
- Add restaurants with custom menus
- Generate random meals per category
- Beautiful SwiftUI interface
- Persistent storage

## Screenshots
![App Screenshot](screenshot.png)

## Requirements
- macOS 12.0+
- Xcode 14.0+

## Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/MealPicker.git
```
Open `MealPicker.xcodeproj` in Xcode and run!
